Nations Foundation will allocate 900,000 U.S. dollars for a
climate change project in China, it was announced here Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The 1 billion dollar foundation with the sole resource from
U.S. businessman Ted Turner, announced Wednesday that it has
earmarked its first batch of 22 million dollars for U.N. women,
population, children and environmental programs.
</P>
