<TEXT>
<P>
TOKYO, May 21 (Xinhua) -- Czech Republic edged out World Cup
qualifier Paraguay 1-0 thanks to Vladimir Smicer's early goal in
the Kirin Cup soccer tournament in Kobe, Japan, on Thursday.
</P>
