<HEADLINE> European Cup Final Winners Since 1955-56 </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, May 21 (Xinhua) -- Following are the European Cup
finals since the competition began in 1955-56 (tabulated under
date, venue, scores):
</P>
<P>
1956 Paris Real Madrid 4 Reims 3
</P>
<P>
1957 Madrid  Real Madrid 2 Fiorentina 0
</P>
<P>
1958 Brussels  Real Madrid 3 AC Milan 2
</P>
<P>
1959 Stuttgart Real Madrid 2 Reims 0
</P>
<P>
1960 Glasgow Real Madrid 7 E. Frankfurt 3
</P>
<P>
1961 Berne Benfica 3 Barcelona 2
</P>
<P>
1962 Amsterdam Benfica 5 Real Madrid 3
</P>
<P>
1963 London  AC Milan 2  Benfica 1
</P>
<P>
1964 Vienna  Internazionale 3 Real Madrid 1
</P>
<P>
1965 Milan Internazionale 1 Benfica 0
</P>
