<HEADLINE> Schaefer Appointed as VfB Stuttgart Coach </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, May 21 (Xinhua) -- Winfried Schaefer has replaced Joachim
Loew to coach European Cup Winners' Cup runners-up VfB Stuttgart
on Thursday following the dismissal of Joachim Loew.
</P>
