unchanged and 124 others untraded.
</P>
<P>
The day's business ballooned to 265.958 million shares valued
at 517.837 million ringgit (138.089 million U.S. dollars) from
147.901 million shares worth 270.335 million ringgit (72.089
million U.S. dollars) on Wednesday.
</P>
