-- The Israeli information center for human rights Betselem has
accused the Israeli security forces of routinely torturing
Palestinians. A report published on Tuesday by Betselem said that
the Israeli secret service Shin Beth exercises tortures on 85
percent of some 850 Palestinians detained by them each year.
</P>
