------
</P>
<P>
ISLAMABAD -- The five underground nuclear tests conducted by
India at Pokhran last week is part of the extremists designs of
India's ruling Bharatiya Janata Party (BJP).
</P>
<P>
This was stated by former Pakistani diplomat Dr. Maqbool Bhatti
while speaking in a live television program broadcast here
Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Bhatti said that the BJP had been saying for many years that
they would develop nuclear weapons which, as they think, are
essential for emerging as a big power in the region as well as in
the world.
</P>
<P>
