<HEADLINE> Norway Trounce Mexico 5-2 in Soccer Friendly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
STOCKHOLM, May 20 (Xinhua) -- Norway trounced Mexico 5-2 in
their last World Cup warm-up match at home on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Coached by Egil Olsen, who is set to retire after the World Cup
finals, the host team scored four goals in the first half to
secure their victory in Oslo.
</P>
