minute but Norway restored their advantage again as defender Ronny
Johnsen slamed home a rebound.
</P>
<P>
Five minutes before the interval, Henning Berg was on target
again from a corner.
</P>
<P>
Both teams slowed their pace in the second half and each team
scored one goal apiece. 
