standard by trouncing Scotland five goals to nothing in their
opener in the 12-team tournament whereas hosts and hot favorites
the Netherlands came from behind to beat New Zealand 2-1.
</P>
<P>
In the day's other games of the women's tourney, Argentina
defeated Olympic silver medalists South Korea 2-1; England downed
India 1-0 and Germany overwhelmed the United States 5-1.
</P>
<P>
